Rating: 4
Tasty and easy! The sliced ribs and stems were a nice addition in terms of texture and color. Like some previous reviewers, I used chicken broth instead of water. I also added a little crushed red pepper with the garlic and a splash of balsamic vinegar just before serving (I like a bit of acid in my greens, and think apple cider vinegar would work well too). Delicious, beautiful, easy and healthy dish -- what more could you ask for?

